00:24:13,787 --> 00:24:15,055
Oh, I guess we can call
a hand surgeon down here.

656
00:24:15,088 --> 00:24:16,890
'Yeah.'

657
00:24:16,923 --> 00:24:18,659
‐ What did you do?
‐ Nothing.

658
00:24:18,692 --> 00:24:20,060
Is he having
a seizure or something?

659
00:24:20,093 --> 00:24:21,762
I‐I, I don't I don't know.

660
00:24:23,630 --> 00:24:27,601
