661
00:24:27,634 --> 00:24:29,970
‐ What does that mean?
‐ Well, there's several kinds.

662
00:24:30,003 --> 00:24:32,573
You don't by chance have any
birds in the house, do you?

663
00:24:32,606 --> 00:24:33,774
How did you know?

664
00:24:33,807 --> 00:24:35,676
