667
00:24:39,946 --> 00:24:42,182
‐ A falcon.
‐ A falcon.

668
00:24:42,215 --> 00:24:44,184
Only thing Daniel
loves more than me.

669
00:24:44,217 --> 00:24:45,819
That's not true.

670
00:24:45,852 --> 00:24:47,888
